data.comment: The referee blows his whistle to start the first-half. Enschede with the kick-off.
Goal! Enschede have got their heads in front thanks to a Danilo strike.
In the minute 1, That's a fine assist from Vaclav Cerny.
Jayden Oosterwolde (Enschede) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
Mark Van der Maarel (Utrecht) gets a yellow card.
In the minute 32, Tyronne Ebuehi is booked for the away team.
Bart Ramselaar is on target to level the scores at 1-1.
The whistle has gone to end the first-half.
In the minute 46, It's Utrecht with the kick-off after the break.
Utrecht take a 2-1 lead thanks to Sander Van de Streek.
Bart Ramselaar with an assist there.
In the minute 55, Jesse Bosch (Enschede) has received a first yellow card.
Giovanni Troupee is on a sub for Mark Van der Maarel for Utrecht.
Julio Pleguezuelo (Enschede) has received a first yellow card.
In the minute 62, Lazaros Lamprou is replacing Vaclav Cerny for the away team.
Ron Jans is making the team's second substitution at Stadion Galgenwaard with Gijs Smal replacing Jayden Oosterwolde.
The away team have replaced Godfried Roemeratoe with Halil Dervisoglu. This is the third substitution made today by Ron Jans.
In the minute 71, Utrecht make their second substitution with Othman Boussaid replacing Moussa Sylla.
The away team replace Dario Dumic with Ramiz Zerrouki.
The whistle has gone to end the second half. The match finishes 2-1.
